data.name: Decompresser_Description
data.value: The one who sees sex as a form of relaxation, an outlet for moments when she feels tense, stressed or upset.

data.name: Decompresser_Name
data.value: Decompresser

data.name: Explorer_Description
data.value: The sex tourist: curious and eager to learn new things. She likes to go beyond her comfort zone and doesn't take sex too seriously.

data.name: Explorer_Name
data.value: Explorer

data.name: FairTrader_Description
data.value: The one that gives extreme importance to the give-receive equation, so that it is balanced. He likes to know that both are attentive to each other's needs and willing to work as a team.

data.name: FairTrader_Name
data.value: Fair Trader

data.name: Giver_Description
data.value: The one who gives more than receives and is in tune with her partner's experiences and needs. A person for whom it is important to know that they can make the other person feel good.

data.name: Giver_Name
data.value: Giver

data.name: Guardian_Description
data.value: The one that emphasizes safety more than anything. This characteristic is typical of those who have suffered some type of trauma or simply need the bond of trust with their partner in moments of intimacy.

data.name: Guardian_Name
data.value: Guardian

data.name: PassionPursuer_Description
data.value: The one who believes that sexual interaction should bring intense, almost animalistic experiences, and that you need to be totally in tune with your partner's energy.

data.name: PassionPursuer_Name
data.value: Passion Pursuer

data.name: PleasureSeeker_Description
data.value: The one that sees physical pleasure as the only objective, considering sex one of the simplest pleasures in life. Likes abundant physical contact, but does not feel the need for the emotional component to do so.

data.name: PleasureSeeker_Name
data.value: Pleasure Seeker

data.name: Prioritizer_Description
data.value: The one who highly values their sex lives and is willing to make sacrifices to maintain a routine, no excuses.

data.name: Prioritizer_Name
data.value: Prioritizer

data.name: Romantic_Description
data.value: The one whose sex is based on a deep connection between the two, it is common to maintain eye contact with the partner or tell him that you love him during sexual intercourse.

data.name: Romantic_Name
data.value: Romantic

data.name: Spiritualist_Description
data.value: To whose sex it is more than what happens in the body, and should be an almost transcendent experience, a communion of souls and not just of bodies.

data.name: Spiritualist_Name
data.value: Spiritualist

data.name: ThrillSeeker_Description
data.value: The one who sees the sexual act as something exciting, almost forbidden. These are the kind of people who need the taboo element, whether that means experiencing something unusual or satisfying a fetish.

data.name: ThrillSeeker_Name
data.value: Thrill Seeker
